com.microfocus.adm.pulse.pluginapi.event.dto

Interface PulseReview


  • public interface PulseReview
    Represents a review within the system.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      String getBody()
      Text that describes the review, normally the commit message of the first changeset.
      List<PulseChangeSet> getChangeSets()
      Set of changesets (in date order) that make up the review.
      String getLabel()
      Label for the review.
      PulseUser getOwner()
      Who currently owns the review, normally the changeset author
      List<PulseRequest> getRequests()
      Set of requests that are associated with the changesets for the review.
      List<PulseReviewer> getReviewers()
      List of reviewers for the review.
      PulseReviewType getReviewType()
      Get the type of review
      PulseReviewState getState()
      Current state of the review, which might be a later state than the notification is for.
      String getTitle()
      Title of the review which can be changed by a user over time.

    • Method Detail

      • getLabel

        String getLabel()
        Label for the review. Unique within the system.
        Returns:
        Never null and can be used as a key for the review.

      • getTitle

        String getTitle()
        Title of the review which can be changed by a user over time.
        Returns:
        Never null.

      • getBody

        String getBody()
        Text that describes the review, normally the commit message of the first changeset.
        Returns:
        Never null.

      • getReviewType

        PulseReviewType getReviewType()
        Get the type of review
        Returns:
        Never null.

      • getState

        PulseReviewState getState()
        Current state of the review, which might be a later state than the notification is for.
        Returns:
        Current state of the review.

      • getOwner

        PulseUser getOwner()
        Who currently owns the review, normally the changeset author
        Returns:
        Null if there is no owner.

      • getReviewers

        List<PulseReviewer> getReviewers()
        List of reviewers for the review.
        Returns:
        List of reviewers

      • getRequests

        List<PulseRequest> getRequests()
        Set of requests that are associated with the changesets for the review. This is captured when the changesets are attached to the review.
        Returns:
        Empty collection if no requests are associated with the review.

      • getChangeSets

        List<PulseChangeSet> getChangeSets()
        Set of changesets (in date order) that make up the review.
        Returns:
        Changesets being reviewed.
